{"tid":2337771,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩英皇原來收埋呢啲咁o既黑絲大波妹","createTime":"2020-12-23T13:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T00:47:13.000Z","uid":22839,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0ea12be7c16754bbf2ab43e684b64a0b2ddb3b","tid":2337771,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201222/418029532105150464861492.jpeg/dl-NMqgYYtEgZSNrDxJiN7obdZwypdbkOqq88jqqvPI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201222%2F418029532105150464861492.jpeg%2Fdl-NMqgYYtEgZSNrDxJiN7obdZwypdbkOqq88jqqvPI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=62722c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201222/_2020122214554079484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201222%2F_2020122214554079484.jpg&h=7b08f24a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵公司（0066）黃竹坑站第五期物業發展項目，今午2時截收發展意向書。港鐵公布，合共接獲37份意向書。綜合消息，有份遞交意向書的財團包括長實（1113）、英皇國際（0163）、華懋集團、爪哇控股（0251）、其士國際（0025），中資方面有碧桂園（2007）、旭輝（0884）、中國金茂控股（0817），另有兩間不知名財團。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，在收到發展意向書後，將編訂經甄選的投標者入圍名單，以邀請發展商及/或財團提交正式標書，並將儘快落實有關招標安排。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">今日遞交意向書的英皇國際高級物業主任蘇穎菁表示</span>，集團認為黃竹坑區發展潛力大，會觀察條款以及補地價金額才決定以獨資或合資形式入標，出價會考慮市況及招標條款等因素。"},{"pid":"a631a8c5944f8488a1344155bc7ffbb4adda3452","tid":2337771,"uid":22310,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T14:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUw8bSb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUw8bSb.jpg&h=361840e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9854a446d9f3b71160b6addad3b708953586beb8","tid":2337771,"uid":22839,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a631a8c5944f8488a1344155bc7ffbb4adda3452","tid":2337771,"uid":22310,"like":